00:37:56,566 --> 00:37:57,566
- Hey. - Hey.

544
00:37:57,566 --> 00:37:58,707
I'm Park Se Mi from Yongpa High School.

545
00:37:58,767 --> 00:37:59,937
You know me, right?

546
00:38:05,964 --> 00:38:07,064
Hey.

547
00:38:09,334 --> 00:38:10,535
Unbelievable.

548
00:38:12,334 --> 00:38:13,564
No, I don't know you.

549
00:38:14,874 --> 00:38:16,604
I noticed you won the Newstagram Queen Contest.

550
00:38:16,705 --> 00:38:18,345
You managed to beat me.

551
00:38:20,814 --> 00:38:23,015
You look better in your photos.

552
00:38:23,314 --> 00:38:26,584
But you look way different from the Lim Ju Kyung I know.

553
00:38:29,155 --> 00:38:30,285
I see.

554
00:38:32,825 --> 00:38:34,524
Why are you in a rush to leave?

555
00:38:34,995 --> 00:38:36,894
It feels like you're avoiding me.

556
00:38:40,265 --> 00:38:41,535
Why isn't Seo Jun coming out?

557
00:38:42,765 --> 00:38:44,205
I don't know.

558
00:38:44,665 --> 00:38:45,834
Let's go, Soo Jin.

559
00:38:47,774 --> 00:38:49,910
I can't believe she's ignoring me.

560
00:38:50,274 --> 00:38:53,104
- Hey, it's Joo Hye Min. - Hye Min!

561
00:38:53,504 --> 00:38:55,144
Where are you going?

562
00:38:55,975 --> 00:38:57,274
Hye Min!

563
00:38:58,415 --> 00:38:59,944
Come over here.

564
00:39:02,354 --> 00:39:04,185
Smile for me. Smile.

565
00:39:06,155 --> 00:39:07,185
Let's go.

566
00:39:12,865 --> 00:39:15,894
Hey, who told you to ignore my calls? Do you have a death wish?

567
00:39:16,865 --> 00:39:19,365
I told you there's nothing going on.

568
00:39:20,104 --> 00:39:23,475
There's nothing going on between her and Seo Jun.

569
00:39:25,674 --> 00:39:27,174
How can you say that even after looking at this?

570
00:39:27,174 --> 00:39:28,845
Are you kidding me?

571
00:39:30,314 --> 00:39:31,845
Hey, I want you...

572
00:39:31,845 --> 00:39:34,984
to keep an eye on Lim Ju Kyung and find out everything about her.

573
00:39:35,415 --> 00:39:37,785
I want to know if she's flirting with anyone...

574
00:39:37,785 --> 00:39:40,685
and if there's anything bad about her personality.

575
00:39:41,294 --> 00:39:43,955
That way, I'll be able to split them apart.

576
00:39:45,394 --> 00:39:46,725
Aren't you going to answer her?

577
00:39:47,694 --> 00:39:48,935
Hye Min!

578
00:39:52,604 --> 00:39:54,305
Were you hitting her?

579
00:39:55,075 --> 00:39:56,504
What are you talking about?

580
00:39:56,504 --> 00:39:59,345
We were just having a chat. Why?

581
00:40:03,214 --> 00:40:06,845
We're supposed to work on our class project today.

582
00:40:08,814 --> 00:40:10,015
Did you forget?

583
00:40:10,555 --> 00:40:11,685
What?

584
00:40:12,484 --> 00:40:13,754
Yes.

585
00:40:14,294 --> 00:40:17,424
She's going somewhere with us today.

586
00:40:22,495 --> 00:40:24,035
The project is more important.

587
00:40:24,805 --> 00:40:26,564
- Let's go. - You're not going anywhere.

588
00:40:33,044 --> 00:40:35,745
Hey. Why are you butting in?

589
00:40:36,274 --> 00:40:38,915
You're from Yongpa High School, aren't you?

590
00:40:50,325 --> 00:40:51,464
Thank you.

591
00:40:53,064 --> 00:40:54,265
I'll go now.

592
00:40:54,665 --> 00:40:55,734
Wait.

593
00:40:57,064 --> 00:40:59,535
You're Ju Kyung, aren't you?

594
00:41:03,734 --> 00:41:05,305
Thanks for helping me.

595
00:41:06,745 --> 00:41:09,615
But you got a lot prettier.

596
00:41:10,345 --> 00:41:12,515
- I didn't recognize... - Just because I helped you,

597
00:41:14,655 --> 00:41:16,055
it doesn't mean I forgave you.

598
00:41:20,624 --> 00:41:22,924
I'm sorry for back then.

599
00:41:24,394 --> 00:41:27,964
I was afraid they'd bully me too if I didn't do as they said.

600
00:41:29,265 --> 00:41:30,635
I was too scared.

601
00:41:34,135 --> 00:41:36,274
I shouldn't have done that to you though.

602
00:41:36,705 --> 00:41:37,944
I'm really sorry.

603
00:41:41,674 --> 00:41:42,845
I don't want the others...

604
00:41:44,415 --> 00:41:46,214
to know what I used to look like.

605
00:41:49,055 --> 00:41:51,055
So don't act like you know me.

606
00:41:51,624 --> 00:41:53,084
I won't.

607
00:41:53,225 --> 00:41:55,254
I won't tell anyone. Don't worry.

608
00:42:08,135 --> 00:42:09,205
And...

609
00:42:12,774 --> 00:42:13,845
What are you doing?

610
00:42:14,745 --> 00:42:15,774
You're knitting?

611
00:42:16,274 --> 00:42:17,785
It's supposed to be therapeutic.

612
00:42:18,444 --> 00:42:19,685
Do something. Anything.

613
00:42:20,845 --> 00:42:23,685
- Why did you want to see me? - To ask you something.

614
00:42:24,555 --> 00:42:27,055
What did you mean when you said Ju Kyung can't tell the others...

615
00:42:27,624 --> 00:42:30,595
that we're going out because of Soo Jin?

616
00:42:31,064 --> 00:42:32,165
Do you know anything about it?

617
00:42:32,265 --> 00:42:33,394
Why?

618
00:42:33,624 --> 00:42:35,234
Ju Kyung has been acting strange.

619
00:42:36,435 --> 00:42:38,165
I think something's up.

620
00:42:38,334 --> 00:42:41,135
Why are you asking me about your girlfriend?

621
00:42:43,035 --> 00:42:44,274
How is she acting strange?

622
00:42:47,374 --> 00:42:48,544
She asked me before...

623
00:42:49,345 --> 00:42:51,415
about a friend of a friend.

624
00:42:52,285 --> 00:42:54,385
That a friend of a friend got a boyfriend,

625
00:42:54,885 --> 00:42:58,084
but that friend of a friend... So, she likes her boyfriend.

626
00:42:58,084 --> 00:43:02,254
So the friend of a friend suddenly said she liked the boyfriend...

627
00:43:02,254 --> 00:43:06,325
So the friend of a friend and the friend of a friend's friend...

628
00:43:07,365 --> 00:43:09,035
Forget it if you don't get it.

629
00:43:10,734 --> 00:43:13,604
What about you? Isn't Soo Jin an old friend?

630
00:43:13,765 --> 00:43:15,604
Will you not to anything that I don't like?

631
00:43:15,935 --> 00:43:17,774
Can you give up your friends for me?

632
00:43:18,345 --> 00:43:19,604
When did she tell you that?

633
00:43:19,705 --> 00:43:21,644
When we made dumplings and clipped each other's...

634
00:43:22,714 --> 00:43:23,944
Don't ask.

635
00:43:24,374 --> 00:43:25,745
I want to erase it from my memory.

636
00:43:29,155 --> 00:43:31,254
Hey. You dropped a stitch.

637
00:43:32,354 --> 00:43:33,484
How can you tell?

638
00:43:33,655 --> 00:43:35,555
I used to knit a long time ago.

639
00:43:36,655 --> 00:43:38,725
You have to undo it and redo it.

640
00:43:38,725 --> 00:43:39,794
Really?

641
00:43:44,805 --> 00:43:45,905
How?

642
00:43:48,035 --> 00:43:49,234
Give it to me.

643
00:43:51,874 --> 00:43:53,504
Can't you even do that right?

644
00:43:54,644 --> 00:43:56,544
No, no. This isn't it.

645
00:43:59,044 --> 00:44:01,854
Soo Ho! I thought we were friends.

646
00:44:02,015 --> 00:44:03,885
I kept begging you to go to the internet cafe with me,

647
00:44:03,885 --> 00:44:05,055
but you refused.

648
00:44:05,285 --> 00:44:06,885
How could you do this to me just because you made up?

649
00:44:07,285 --> 00:44:08,694
How can love... No.

650
00:44:09,555 --> 00:44:10,825
How can friendship change?

651
00:44:10,825 --> 00:44:12,024
What's his problem?

652
00:44:12,865 --> 00:44:13,924
Darn it.

653
00:44:13,924 --> 00:44:15,595
- Do you know how to knit? - Yes.

654
00:44:15,894 --> 00:44:17,635
I knitted a scarf for Doo Ah.

655
00:44:17,765 --> 00:44:18,865
Were you knitting?

656
00:44:20,765 --> 00:44:22,575
- Put this in. - Put this in.

657
00:44:22,575 --> 00:44:23,635
- Loop it. - Loop it.

658
00:44:23,635 --> 00:44:24,905
- And... - Seo Jun!

659
00:44:25,544 --> 00:44:26,805
How could you?

660
00:44:26,905 --> 00:44:30,044
You refused to go singing with me to do this?

661
00:44:30,415 --> 00:44:33,385
How could friendship change?

662
00:44:36,984 --> 00:44:38,155
I'm starved.

663
00:44:40,185 --> 00:44:41,495
Sorry for making you wait.

664
00:44:41,655 --> 00:44:43,754
- How was your class? - Good.

665
00:44:44,424 --> 00:44:46,165
Why did you come all this way?

666
00:44:46,165 --> 00:44:47,394
To go home with you.

667
00:44:51,834 --> 00:44:54,165
- Ju Kyung. - Yes?

668
00:44:54,365 --> 00:44:58,044
Do you feel good or bad?

669
00:44:58,504 --> 00:44:59,745
Why do you ask?

670
00:44:59,874 --> 00:45:03,644
Just because. Do you feel good or bad?

671
00:45:06,785 --> 00:45:07,915
Good.

672
00:45:13,124 --> 00:45:14,854
Won't you tell me what it is?

673
00:45:17,124 --> 00:45:18,225
Actually...

674
00:45:19,424 --> 00:45:21,635
A kid from my old school transferred in.

675
00:45:22,564 --> 00:45:23,635
What?

676
00:45:23,734 --> 00:45:25,234
It wasn't because of Soo Jin?

677
00:45:25,734 --> 00:45:29,104
I thought she wouldn't recognize me, but she did.

678
00:45:30,004 --> 00:45:31,035
Are you okay?

679
00:45:31,805 --> 00:45:33,245
I'm nervous,

680
00:45:33,944 --> 00:45:36,015
but she says she won't tell anyone.

681
00:45:36,475 --> 00:45:37,615
You must've been scared.

682
00:45:39,544 --> 00:45:40,685
A bit.

683
00:45:42,584 --> 00:45:44,455
But I'm really okay now.

684
00:45:54,365 --> 00:45:55,535
Aren't you hungry?

685
00:45:55,765 --> 00:45:57,165
Should we get something to eat?

686
00:45:59,305 --> 00:46:00,464
What should we get?

687
00:46:01,374 --> 00:46:02,535
Something you like.

688
00:46:10,575 --> 00:46:12,515
I didn't get prettier.

689
00:46:15,714 --> 00:46:18,055
I'm breaking out again.

690
00:46:27,524 --> 00:46:29,135
It's so annoying.

691
00:46:30,394 --> 00:46:32,265
Hee Kyung, do you want to go on a blind date?

692
00:46:32,535 --> 00:46:34,774
The pork trotter restaurant owner's son's friend...

693
00:46:34,774 --> 00:46:35,874
I have a boyfriend.

694
00:46:36,774 --> 00:46:38,475
- You do? - You do?

695
00:46:38,905 --> 00:46:40,975
Are you lying to avoid going on a blind date?

696
00:46:41,644 --> 00:46:43,015
It's true.

697
00:46:43,674 --> 00:46:46,544
Oh my gosh. How long has it been? What does he do?

698
00:46:46,544 --> 00:46:47,785
Is it good looking? How old is he?

699
00:46:48,555 --> 00:46:51,385
It's a secret. I'll introduce you when I think it's time.

700
00:46:51,484 --> 00:46:52,584
Do you have a picture?

701
00:46:52,785 --> 00:46:55,055
I can tell what he's like just by looking at his face.

702
00:46:55,055 --> 00:46:57,854
I'm dying of curiosity.

703
00:46:57,854 --> 00:46:59,524
What is he like?

704
00:47:01,694 --> 00:47:04,365
- My grapefruit. - Grapefruit?

705
00:47:04,564 --> 00:47:07,564
He gets cuter and cuter the more I look at him.

706
00:47:08,174 --> 00:47:10,604
His face is fruity.

707
00:47:11,905 --> 00:47:13,075
Fruity?

708
00:47:13,174 --> 00:47:14,674
I'm home.

709
00:47:14,674 --> 00:47:16,475
Welcome home. Come eat.

710
00:47:17,374 --> 00:47:19,944
A fly has no right to eat.

711
00:47:25,524 --> 00:47:29,055
Lim Ju Kyung, please come to the auditorium.

712
00:47:29,555 --> 00:47:31,055
Ju Kyung!

713
00:47:32,124 --> 00:47:33,424
She looks so pretty.

714
00:47:33,424 --> 00:47:36,095
You're doing great, Ju Kyung!

715
00:47:36,095 --> 00:47:37,435
You look so pretty!

716
00:47:37,435 --> 00:47:40,035
An angel has descended!

717
00:47:41,035 --> 00:47:44,334
She is lighting up the stage.

718
00:47:44,334 --> 00:47:46,044
Look at her perfect skin!

719
00:47:47,174 --> 00:47:49,575
How did this happen to me?

720
00:47:50,874 --> 00:47:53,984
- She's the perfect school model. - I know.

721
00:47:53,984 --> 00:47:55,155
Hold on.

722
00:47:55,814 --> 00:47:58,325
Must I do this?

723
00:47:58,754 --> 00:48:02,694
Isn't the student body president or the top student usually the model?

724
00:48:02,694 --> 00:48:06,225
Yes. But Ju Kyung, they don't want to do it.

725
00:48:06,225 --> 00:48:07,325
What?

726
00:48:07,865 --> 00:48:09,834
But why me of all people...

727
00:48:09,834 --> 00:48:10,995
What do you mean?

728
00:48:11,805 --> 00:48:14,035
I hear you're our star.

729
00:48:14,035 --> 00:48:17,535
You're the star among stars, so you might as well do it.

730
00:48:17,535 --> 00:48:20,004
The face of Saebom!

731
00:48:23,575 --> 00:48:25,185
Let's try another pose.

732
00:48:25,385 --> 00:48:27,185
You look so pretty!

733
00:48:30,584 --> 00:48:31,825
You look pretty!

734
00:48:32,455 --> 00:48:34,754
Do it right. Check your form.

735
00:48:35,555 --> 00:48:39,194
Will we see your face when we go into your homepage?

736
00:48:39,265 --> 00:48:43,165
The face of Saebom, Lim Ju Kyung.

737
00:48:43,265 --> 00:48:46,705
Stop that. Please. I'm not the face.

738
00:48:46,805 --> 00:48:48,575
Can't you do that right?

739
00:48:48,575 --> 00:48:51,905
3, 4, 5.

740
00:48:52,245 --> 00:48:55,044
Did they make up after being hospitalized together?

741
00:48:55,274 --> 00:48:56,944
Is it because they shared each other's pain?

742
00:48:57,245 --> 00:48:58,915
- Seven. - You're pulling too hard.

743
00:48:58,915 --> 00:49:00,185
Do it right.

744
00:49:00,185 --> 00:49:01,584
- Do it already. - Fine.

745
00:49:01,584 --> 00:49:03,685
- Again. - Darn it.

746
00:49:03,685 --> 00:49:05,584
- One. - Why is it one again?

747
00:49:07,484 --> 00:49:08,754
You guys will never finish at this rate.

748
00:49:08,754 --> 00:49:10,055
(From Park Se Mi, You've got a new message.)

749
00:49:10,794 --> 00:49:11,865
Who is it?

750
00:49:12,794 --> 00:49:13,924
It's nothing.

751
00:49:13,924 --> 00:49:16,394
Don't fool around. Do it right.

752
00:49:16,694 --> 00:49:18,435
What are you doing?

753
00:49:24,475 --> 00:49:26,504
What are you doing? Why are you taking my pictures?

754
00:49:27,104 --> 00:49:28,274
Because you look cool.

755
00:49:30,115 --> 00:49:31,544
Don't you like Soo Ho?

756
00:49:31,984 --> 00:49:33,385
I do. So?

757
00:49:34,144 --> 00:49:35,885
Don't you know he's going out with Ju Kyung?

758
00:49:35,885 --> 00:49:36,915
I do.

759
00:49:36,915 --> 00:49:39,725
You like her although you know. Am I wrong?

760
00:49:52,305 --> 00:49:53,935
(- Give me Ju Kyung's pictures. - Then give me Seo Jun's.)

761
00:49:58,444 --> 00:50:00,845
(Park Se Mi)

762
00:50:10,055 --> 00:50:12,484
It's like one would take of a real boyfriend. Thanks.

763
00:50:12,685 --> 00:50:15,155
Why do you want her photos though?

764
00:50:30,874 --> 00:50:32,144
Are these all you have?

765
00:50:33,575 --> 00:50:34,705
All that running made me hungry.

766
00:50:34,845 --> 00:50:35,874
Let's get a snack.

767
00:50:36,345 --> 00:50:37,544
What should we have?

768
00:50:38,845 --> 00:50:40,015
Ju Kyung!

769
00:50:41,385 --> 00:50:42,814
I'm sorry.

770
00:50:45,655 --> 00:50:46,825
Are you all right?

771
00:51:17,185 --> 00:51:19,254
What's wrong? Are you looking for something?

772
00:51:19,455 --> 00:51:21,955
Gosh, I think I've lost my necklace.

773
00:51:22,825 --> 00:51:24,455
Where did I put it? I don't think I took it off.

774
00:51:24,455 --> 00:51:26,365
- The one you have on every day? - Yes.

775
00:51:26,524 --> 00:51:28,165
When did you last see it?

776
00:51:28,595 --> 00:51:30,135
I definitely had it on this morning.

777
00:51:30,135 --> 00:51:32,535
Maybe it got loose during PE.

778
00:51:33,135 --> 00:51:35,435
- You think? - Come on. I'll help you.

779
00:51:35,874 --> 00:51:36,975
Thanks.

780
00:51:51,415 --> 00:51:53,225
Where did it go?

781
00:51:59,024 --> 00:52:00,424
I told her not to look for it.

782
00:52:01,265 --> 00:52:02,894
She'll be here all night.

783
00:52:09,174 --> 00:52:10,535
As if it would still be here.

784
00:52:12,374 --> 00:52:13,644
Someone probably took it.

785
00:52:13,975 --> 00:52:15,915
It wasn't at Lost and Found.

786
00:52:15,975 --> 00:52:17,915
Besides, I trust the students here.

787
00:52:18,415 --> 00:52:19,915
Check out your pride for this school.

788
00:52:20,345 --> 00:52:21,544
Because you're the face of it now?

789
00:52:21,814 --> 00:52:22,984
Of course not.

790
00:52:23,515 --> 00:52:25,754
Now move over. You might step on it.

791
00:52:25,825 --> 00:52:27,024
Want some help finding it?

792
00:52:27,624 --> 00:52:28,754
What will I get in return?

793
00:52:30,655 --> 00:52:31,894
I'll treat you to spicy tteokbokki.

794
00:52:32,865 --> 00:52:34,495
Buy something else, will you?

795
00:52:34,924 --> 00:52:37,495
You like it though. Isn't it your favorite?

796
00:52:37,495 --> 00:52:40,935
Whatever. If I find it for you, you'll pay me big time.

797
00:52:41,464 --> 00:52:42,475
Got it.

798
00:52:47,205 --> 00:52:48,274
Found it!

799
00:52:48,944 --> 00:52:49,944
Really?

800
00:52:51,444 --> 00:52:53,084
50 cents. Sweet, isn't it?

801
00:52:54,115 --> 00:52:55,354
Seriously?

802
00:53:02,394 --> 00:53:04,894
I mean it this time. Is this your necklace?

803
00:53:05,064 --> 00:53:06,424
Did you find it?

804
00:53:11,135 --> 00:53:12,435
Just go home already.

805
00:53:12,604 --> 00:53:14,964
Fine. I'll look for it seriously, okay?

806
00:53:14,964 --> 00:53:17,035
I don't appreciate the teasing.

807
00:53:17,635 --> 00:53:20,245
Soo Ho gave it to me, so I must find it.

808
00:53:23,075 --> 00:53:25,814
- I'm leaving. - You promised to help me find it.

809
00:53:25,814 --> 00:53:27,115
I'm a busy man.

810
00:53:27,415 --> 00:53:29,385
Must you look for this when it's this cold?

811
00:53:30,714 --> 00:53:32,984
Is Soo Ho upset because you've lost it?

812
00:53:33,225 --> 00:53:34,354
Of course not.

